high_descs: Pick up the dirty towel next to the sink
Turn around and face the sink
Wash the dirty towel in the sink
Turn around and face the sinks
Place the cleaned towel in the middle of the sinks
anns.task_desc: Place a washed towel in the middle of two sinks

high_descs: Walk over to the right side of the sink counter.
Pick up the dirty blue rag off of the counter.
Walk up to the rightmost sink.
Put the dirty rag in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean blue rag.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Put the clean blue rag on the counter in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean blue rag on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the cloth from the counter.
Move to the left and face the sink on the right.
Put the cloth in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the cloth up from the sink.
Move to the left and face the counter in between the two sinks.
Put the cloth on the counter between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cloth on the counter.
